name: USDC Bridged
description: USDC Bridged (USDC.c) is a wrapped version of USD Coin deployed on Binance Smart Chain, Solana, and Ethereum. It is fully backed by on-chain and off-chain reserves and transparently pegged to $1. Designed for speed and efficiency, USDC.c enables low-cost, high-speed DeFi transactions and cross-chain payments with strong stability.
